---
import Header from "../components/services/header.astro";
import Artist from "../components/services/artist.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import conceptAndCreative1 from "../assets/services/concept-creative1.png";
import conceptAndCreative2 from "../assets/services/concept-creative2.png";
import damianLazarus from "../assets/services/damian-lazarus.png";
import hernanCattaneo from "../assets/services/hernan-cattaneo.png";
import morcheeba from "../assets/services/morcheeba.png";
import mihaiPopoviciu from "../assets/services/mihai-popoviciu.png";
import designAndMarketing1 from "../assets/services/design-marketing1.png";
import designAndMarketing2 from "../assets/services/design-marketing2.png";
import designAndMarketing3 from "../assets/services/design-marketing3.png";
import designAndMarketing4 from "../assets/services/design-marketing4.png";
import eventProduction1 from "../assets/services/event-production1.png";
import eventProduction2 from "../assets/services/event-production2.png";
import eventProduction3 from "../assets/services/event-production3.png";
import eventProduction4 from "../assets/services/event-production4.png";
import artCuration from "../assets/services/art-curation.png";
import horizontalLogo from "../assets/festa-logo-horizontal.png";
---

<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-y-7 bg-black pt-10">
  <h2 class="letter-spacing-[10%] bg-white px-1 font-mono text-3xl">
    SERVICES
  </h2>
  <p class="px-8 text-center text-xl font-light text-white">
    From intimate gatherings to large-scale festivals
    <span class="font-bold"> our every event is carefully planned </span> managed,
    and brought to life with a
    <span class="font-bold"> clear vision and strong execution. </span>
  </p>

  <!-- Concept & Creative -->
  <Header>Concept & Creative</Header>
  <p class="px-8 text-center text-xl leading-5 font-light text-white">
    Every event starts with a strong idea. From storytelling and branding to
    unique formats, the focus is on developing concepts that give each project
    its own identity. Whether shaping a festival, brand activation, or cultural
    event, the goal is to create something original that connects with the
    audience.
  </p>
  <div class="w-full">
    <Image src={conceptAndCreative1} alt="concept and creative 1" />
    <Image src={conceptAndCreative2} alt="concept and creative 2" />
  </div>

  <!--  Artist Booking -->
  <Header>Artist Bookings</Header>
  <p class="px-8 text-center text-xl leading-5 font-light text-white">
    Bringing world-class talent to the stage is key to any successful event.
    With experience in booking international DJs, musicians, and
    multidisciplinary artists, the network includes names like John Malkovich,
    Isabella Rossellini, Morcheeba, Nouvelle Vague, Hernan Cattaneo, and Damian
    Lazarus. From negotiations to full logistical support, everything is handled
    from start to finish.
  </p>
  <div class="grid w-full grid-cols-2">
    <Artist image={damianLazarus} name="Damian Lazarus" />
    <Artist image={hernanCattaneo} name="Hernan Cattaneo" />
    <Artist image={mihaiPopoviciu} name="Mihai Popoviciu" />
    <Artist image={morcheeba} name="Morcheeba" />
  </div>
  <p class="text-center text-lg text-white">AND MANY MORE...</p>

  <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
    <Image class="h-10 w-[229px]" src={horizontalLogo} alt="horizontal logo" />
  </div>

  <!--  Design & Marketing -->
  <Header>Design & Marketing</Header>
  <p class="px-8 text-center text-xl leading-5 font-light text-white">
    A strong visual identity and the right strategy ensure that every event
    makes an impact. From branding, stage design, and digital campaigns to PR
    and media partnerships, everything is carefully crafted to reach the right
    audience. Creative direction meets modern marketing, delivering the
    visibility and engagement each project deserves.
  </p>
  <div class="grid w-full grid-cols-2">
    <Image src={designAndMarketing1} alt="design and marketing 1" />
    <Image src={designAndMarketing2} alt="design and marketing 2" />
    <Image src={designAndMarketing3} alt="design and marketing 3" />
    <Image src={designAndMarketing4} alt="design and marketing 4" />
  </div>

  <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
    <Image class="h-10 w-[229px]" src={horizontalLogo} alt="horizontal logo" />
  </div>

  <!--  Event Production -->
  <Header>Event Production</Header>
  <p class="px-8 text-center text-xl leading-5 font-light text-white">
    From small gatherings to large-scale festivals, flawless execution is at the
    core of every project. This includes venue selection, technical setup,
    logistics, and on-site management, ensuring a smooth experience for artists,
    guests, and audiences. Every detail is handled with efficiency and
    precision.
  </p>
  <div class="grid w-full grid-cols-2">
    <Image src={eventProduction1} alt="event production 1" />
    <Image src={eventProduction2} alt="event production 2" />
    <Image src={eventProduction3} alt="event production 3" />
    <Image src={eventProduction4} alt="event production 4" />
  </div>

  <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
    <Image class="h-10 w-[229px]" src={horizontalLogo} alt="horizontal logo" />
  </div>

  <!--  Art Curation -->
  <Header>Art Curation</Header>
  <p class="px-8 text-center text-xl leading-5 font-light text-white">
    Merging music, space, and visual art, each project integrates installations,
    exhibitions, and performances to add another dimension to the experience.
    Whether selecting site-specific installations, large-scale visuals, or
    conceptual exhibitions, the goal is to bring fresh artistic perspectives
    into the events.
  </p>
  <div class="w-full">
    <Image src={artCuration} alt="art curation" />
  </div>

  <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
    <Image class="h-10 w-[229px]" src={horizontalLogo} alt="horizontal logo" />
  </div>
</div>
